<H2><U><img align=top src="vinelarge.jpg"><font size=6><a name="tribe">Haisla Language Resources</a></font></u></H2>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://www.native-languages.org/haisla_words.htm
">Haisla Vocabulary</a></b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Our list of vocabulary words in the Haisla language, with comparison to words in other Wakashan languages.
<BR>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://www-unix.oit.umass.edu/~ebach/dye.htm
">Haisla Language Text</a></b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Haisla story with English translation and an audio recording.
<BR>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://www.languagegeek.com/wakashan/xaislakala.html
">Xa'islak'ala</a></b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Haisla orthography and text example.
<BR>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://www.cthr-mcdp.com/plaques/Haisla.html
">Haisla Language Plaque</a></b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Canadian human rights tribute written in Haisla.
<BR>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://www.ethnologue.com/show_language.asp?code=has
">Ethnologue: Haisla</a>:</b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Demographic information about the Haisla language.
<BR>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://multitree.org/codes/has.html
">Haisla Language Tree</a>:</b> <br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Theories about Haisla's language relationships compiled by Linguist List.
<BR>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://wals.info/languoid/lect/wals_code_hsl
">Haisla Language Structures</a>:</b> <br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Haisla linguistic profile and academic bibliography.
<BR>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"  ALT="*"><B><A HREF="
http://curtis.library.northwestern.edu/curtis/viewPage.cgi?showp=1&size=2&id=nai.10.book.00000415&volume=10#nav
">Kwakiutl Comparative Vocabulary</a>:</b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Early 20th-century wordlists of Haisla compared to other Wakashan languages.
<BR>

